        <updateDate>2008-07-21T21:47:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Improving Methods to Promote Regular Occurrences of the Verification of Employability Status Act of 2008 - Amends the Illegal Immigration Reform and Immigrant Responsibility Act of 1996 to eliminate the pilot program status of the E-verify (employment authorization) program.</p> <p>Revises confirmation provisions. Adds provisions respecting fraudulent documentation and sanctions. Provides that information posters required to be displayed shall be written only in English.</p> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
